A hybrid self service portal to provision & manage VM's on VMware and solusVM in a single environment !!

Front end:
	- basic UI with PHP/HTML
Back end:
	- VMware - python, pysphere(Python API for interacting with the vSphere Web Services SDK)
	- solusVM - PHP, solusVM API

List of supported operations:

VMware:

	- Create Virtual Machines from Template
	- Power on a Virtual machine
	- Power off a Virtual machine
	- Reset a Virtual machine
	- Suspend a Virtual machine
	- Guest Power Operations
	- Resize Virtual machine Resources
	- Add disk to a Virtual machine
	- List IP Addresses of all machines
	- Assign IP Address to a machine
	- Snapshot operations
	- Clone VM
	- Migrate a VM
	- Activate Windows License against a KMS server
	- Virtual Machine Information
	- VCenter Information
	- VNC Operations - enable/view/disable
	- VM Power Status


solusVM:

	- List all the Clients
	- List all the Templates
	- Get Server Status by ID
	- List all Servers in a node
	- List all nodes
	- List all plans of a node
	- List ISO
	- Terminate a server
	- Power Operations


VMware scripts - dir scripts/misc/
solusVM  - dir solusvm/
index - choose.php
